						               													<description>Dragons vs Unicorns is a 2 - 4 player deck building game.&amp;#10;This is a very fast paced deck builder, game time under 30mins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game play:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Dragons vs Unicorns, you race against your opponents to gather reputation and hire Mercenaries from the Mercenary guild.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn you will play out your hand, activate abilities, and draft cards into your deck. Place enchantments for powerful upgrades, send out your Mercenary meeples for more abilities, and destroy your opposition!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Keeping track of your life total is breeze with the dual dial life counters, and keep an eye out for a chance to activate Elemental synergies! Build the strongest army, and help protect the kingdom!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Elemental synergies can be activated by playing cards with matching elemental types, each of the 4 elements, excel at a particular task. &amp;#10; Life - will heal you and allow you to draw more cards  &amp;#10;Darkness - will allow you to destroy your opponent's hand&amp;#10;Fire -will allow you to draw more cards, and deal extra damage for each other fire card. &amp;#10;Water - will allow you to remove unwanted cards, making your deck more effective.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mix and match more than one element to build decks that synergize in unexpected ways.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each element has cards that can act as mounts allowing you to send our your mercenary meeples, to gain even more effects. Place enchantments to shield you and your meeples from your opponents. Is your opponent's mercenary meeples, causing you grief? Destroy them!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To win, drop your opponents health to &amp;quot;0&amp;quot;, empty out the mercenary guild, or bring your life total over 99. The path to victory is varied, which will your choose?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game includes everything needed for 2-4 players!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
